metadata.name: unauthorized intervention
metadata.description:
Can a person live day and night at the same time? Can he seem happy when he is unhappy, and unhappy when he is happy? Do you really need to do this? Unfortunately, with unauthorized interventions in the life cycle, they can make us look happy when we are unhappy and unhappy when we are happy.
